==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Picea
<hw>Pic"e*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., the pitch
pine, from <ets>pix</ets>, <ets>picis</ets>, pitch.]</ety>
<fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of coniferous trees of the northern
hemisphere, including the Norway spruce and the American black and white
spruces. These trees have pendent cones, which do not readily fall to
pieces, in this and other respects differing from the firs.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Picene</ent>⟦br⟧
